libnmath
--------
Copyright 2010, 2011 (c) Papadopoulos Nikos <nikpapas@gmail.com>

About
-----
The nemesis math library implements a variety of datatypes and utilities 
that are useful in graphics related applications. The library provides a 
double interface in c and c++.

libnmath is based on Nuclear's libvmath [http://gfxtools.sourceforge.net]
